[asy]
unitsize(0.6 cm);

pair A, B, C;

A = (3,-5);
B = (-2,0);
C = (1,-6);

draw(A--B);
draw(C--A,Arrow(6));
draw(C--B,Arrow(6));
draw(A--(A + B - C)--B,dashed);

label("$\mathbf{v}$", (A + C)/2, SE);
label("$\mathbf{w}$", (B + C)/2, SW);
dot("$A$", A, E);
dot("$B$", B, W);
dot("$C$", C, S);
[/asy]

The area of the parallelogram determined by $\mathbf{v}$ and $\mathbf{w}$ is
